metadata.name: Mango Néctar
metadata.description:
Step into The Cariberse and let these 2 characters show you the place from a local point of view. 


❥ Herencia: You are in luck! cuz today is -water day- and we get to use the tank as a lil’ pool. You can get in if you want <3

❥ Instinto: or... you can help me feed the macaws? Around 3-5pm they come back to their trees. They’re used to us. Grab a mango! 

❥ Instinto: "does this macaw have a name?" you ask lol yeah, it's Bingo.
